    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini salvalvatoris nostri Iesu Christi Dei eterni. Domini
                            <persName key="#Princeps #Marquis/duke #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            ref="#people/3002">Iordanis</persName> divina ordinante clementia
                        Capuanorum <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs> petitioni dilecti sui clementer
                        favet. Notum sit omnibus sancte et catholice Ecclesie filiis me Iordanum,
                        quem ad hoc divina gratia promovit in principem, ut ecclesiarum defensor
                        atque ditator existam, pro salute et redemptione anime <rs key="#Princeps"
                            >principis</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps #parentOf" ref="#people/3001">Richardi</persName>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">patris</rs> mei et <persName key="#parentOf"
                            ref="#people/3003">Fredesinde</persName>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">matris</rs> mee et parentum meorum, et pro salute mea et
                            <persName key="#Principissa #marriage" ref="#people/3011"
                            >Gaytelgrimme</persName>
                        <rs key="#Principissa">principisse</rs>
                        <rs key="#marriage">uxoris</rs> mee et filiorum meorum, prudentia ipsius
                        uxoris mee interveniente, dedisse et concessisse <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3046">Sancti Angeli quod
                            dicitur ad Arcum Diane</orgName>, subditum <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancti Benedicti
                            Montis Casini</orgName>, cui domnus <persName
                            key="#Abbots #Personal_rank" ref="#people/2416">Oderisius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> preest, et domno <persName key="#Prevosts"
                            ref="#people/4216">Girardo</persName> eiusdem monasterio Sancti Angeli
                            <rs key="#Prevosts">preposito</rs> suisque successoribus in perpetuum,
                        pro servitio hospitum, <rs
                            key="#Chestnuts #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >castanetum</rs> quod est ad <placeName key="#Chestnuts"
                            ref="#places/4532">Sanctum Georgium</placeName> prope <placeName
                            ref="#places/4530">Battiticzum</placeName>, habens taliter <rs
                            key="#Fines">fines</rs>: ab uno capite est cripta Sancti Georgii et
                        trivium Sancti Martini de Lave, et qualiter vadit per cavam que dicitur via
                        antiqua et redit per terram que dicitur Iohannis Coppule et intrat in viam
                        publicam que vadit ad Limatulam et redit ad predictam criptam et trivium; et
                            <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">homines</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terras</rs> que fuerunt <persName><name ref="Petrus de Rosella">Petri
                                de Rosella</name></persName> et <rs key="#siblingOf">germani</rs>
                        eius, sicut cartula prescripti patris mei continere videtur de oblatione
                        quam fecit eidem monasterio Sancti Angeli, qui sunt apud <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Coloni/tenants" ref="#places/4533">Sanctum
                            Herasmum</placeName>, <rs key="#Uncertain_tradition">et <rs
                                key="#Landed_possessions">terras</rs> que sunt in <placeName
                                key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/4534">Ponticello</placeName>
                            et in <placeName ref="#places/4535" key="#Landed_possessions"
                                >Casalva</placeName> et in <placeName key="#Landed_possessions"
                                ref="#places/4536">Sancto Prisco</placeName>, et ubicumque sunt
                            terre ipse in partibus <placeName ref="#places/2823"
                                key="#Landed_possessions">veteris Capue</placeName> vel
                            ubicumque</rs>. Et concedo prescripto monasterio Sancti Angeli ut <rs
                            key="#Privileges">si aliquis homo venerit ex aliis partibus, liber sit
                            ad habitandum in terris ipsius monasterii Sancti Angeli ad servitium
                            fratrum faciendum</rs>, ut nullus homo eos audeat inquietare, sed securi
                        serviant monasterio et eius rectoribus, ad possessionem et dominationem
                        predicti monasterii Sancti Angeli et prescripti domni Girardi prepositi
                        suorumque successorum, remota omnia contrarietate et molestatione mortalium
                        omnium. Quod siquis cuius mee concessionis violator esse presumpserit, <rs
                            key="#Penalty">centum auri optimi libras</rs> persolbat, medietatem meo
                        fisco et medietatem prescripto monasterio Sancti Angeli suisque rectoribus,
                        et soluta pena, hoc scriptum firmum et inviolabile maneat in perpetuum. Et
                        in firmus credatur et diligentius observetur, manu mea subscripsi et meo
                        sigillo decoravi. Signum domni <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Marquis/duke #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            ref="#people/3002">Iordani</persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">gloriosissimi</rs> principis.
                        IORDANVS. Ex iussione prescripti principis scripsi ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Judge" ref="#people/3005">Cansolinus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> in anno principatus ipsius tricesimo primo et
                        XXVI anno <rs key="#Marquis/duke #Marca/ducatum">ducatus</rs> eius
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/2343"><geogName
                                key="#Marca/ducatum" ref="#estates/3001"
                            >Gaiete</geogName></placeName>. Data IIII kalendas Februarii, anno ab
                        incarnatione Domini nostri Iesu Christi .M. LXXX nono. Scriptum <placeName
                            key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capue</placeName> per indictionem
                        duodecimam.</ab>
